FinCon is an annual conference for financial media. Founded in 2011, the annual conference moves to a new location each year and attracts over 1,000 attendees. Founded by Phillip Taylor of PTMoney, the event claims to be "the worldâ€™s largest Financial Content Expo." The conference hosts speakers, workshops, networking sessions, and social events. Noteworthy past speakers include Farnoosh Torabi, Darren Rowse, Noah Kagan, and Eric Rosenberg.
